                <li>Enhanced UI for a more user-friendly experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="technologies-used" class="container mt-4">
    <h2>Featured Technologies</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>ASP.NET for seamless application development.</li>
        <li>MVC Design Patterns for a clean and organized codebase.</li>
        <li>CSS and Bootstrap classes for personalized UI customization.</li>
        <li>Secure Login and Registration Authentication for data protection.</li>
        <li>SQL Database to efficiently store and manage workout data.</li>
    </ul>
</section>

